{"tid":353159,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九寨溝強震捐款給中國人嗎？ PTT他提3大拒捐理由被推爆","createTime":"2017-08-09T10:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T11:07:19.000Z","uid":35790,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"90b65e250387367b9f61e137ad9d7d8a69af5b4f","tid":353159,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T10:53:03.000Z","msg":"九寨溝強震捐款給中國人嗎？ 他提3大拒捐理由被推爆<br />\n<br />\n2017-08-09 15:55<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國四川省九寨溝昨晚間發生芮氏規模7.0地震，造成多人死傷，是否捐款震災給中國，引起鄉民討論；PTT上一名鄉民提出三大理由，「根本不用捐錢給他們」，獲得「推爆」回響！<br />\n<br />\n鄉民「DarkHolbach」提出<span style=\"color: red;\">第一個理由就是「看中共如何處理豆腐渣工程」</span>。他表示，中共想封鎖消息就封鎖，依舊沒學到教訓，而那些揭發豆腐渣工程的人，如黃琦、譚作人等人，最後卻分別被「非法持有國家機密文件罪」、「煽動顛覆國家政權罪」等罪被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">再來的原因就是「中國先前怎麼對我們的」</span>，「DarkHolbach」說，台灣當年921大地震時，中國官方阻擋俄羅斯等國家物資、救難隊來台救人，藉此要開放三通，還趁機開立「中國台灣省救災專戶」捐款，以宣傳台灣為中國一省。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第三個原因則是「中國嚴重貪汙腐敗」</span>，「DarkHolbach」以香港為例，2008年的汶川地震，港府及民間捐款逾200億，但5年後雅安地震，卻瀰漫一片拒捐聲浪，不少民眾被貪腐情況嚇到，擔心捐款被貪官中飽私囊。<br />\n<br />\n「DarkHolbach」也感嘆說，別指望中國的「友誼」，「中國有好人，但那些『好人』未必會對你好」。其他鄉民看到後熱烈回覆，「真的不要捐 那些錢只會跑到垃圾官身上」、<span style=\"color: red;\">「捐錢讓他們多幾根飛彈打台灣 傻子才捐」</span>、「去找個四川來的問問阿 誰知道台灣捐過那麼多錢」、<span style=\"color: red;\">「捐給中國人，中國人轉頭 還不是照說，台灣是中國的」</span>、「香港真的是被騙的最佳例子 台灣不要重蹈覆轍」、「寧願把錢拿去幫台灣弱勢」；還有人說，「捐錢不如捐物資」、「道義上是該幫助他們 但錢的事輪不到我們煩惱」。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/2157641\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F2157641&d=ZU57oDN5X%2FMBXUiFlfuwvjACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=9441c673\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F2157641&h=f2d0fc73\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/2157641</a>"},{"pid":"a45bf09249b151315322c056454034a61b6258f5","tid":353159,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T10:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d81da8baf3fb641e9f6e8a260e6be3735760987a","tid":353159,"uid":76181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T10:54:59.000Z","msg":"嗰陣香港仲要億億聲咁捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd3461a23a899ac1850bc6993f805b3e41557d3","tid":353159,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T10:56:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 向捐款說不<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e77c7d002fa694357d1b36b80b027d788c249c1","tid":353159,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T10:57:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嗰陣香港仲要億億聲咁捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中國咁強大都要搵人接濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4458daf79f0799f7f32ea3d95ae7050f9f8838f","tid":353159,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T11:03:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「捐錢讓他們多幾根飛彈打台灣 傻子才捐」</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「捐給中國人，中國人轉頭 還不是照說，台灣是中國的」</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://oi37.tinypic.com/vy8nme.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Foi37.tinypic.com%2Fvy8nme.jpg&h=8e952ad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQCQLW87c_jCuQwPEQReiDKnfxDyexApSpIJZe8ksjPd-Sjt9VJDQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcQCQLW87c_jCuQwPEQReiDKnfxDyexApSpIJZe8ksjPd-Sjt9VJDQ&h=892dd45d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91b55e506ed299ca177c1cc1d380c4fe78be3600","tid":353159,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T11:03:32.000Z","